                  </hi> The prisoner had been in Mr. Penson's employ one week. On that Saturday night he went to the stable with me, and helped to take the horse out of the cart, and wash his legs—while I was rubbing</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184905070035"></xptr>
               <p>him down, the prisoner walked up and down—I stopped about ten minutes; he came out with me.(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
